Mr. Booth then proceeded in the following manner:  “I perceive, sir, you are but just arrived in this dismal place, which is, indeed, rendered more detestable by the wretches who inhabit it than by any other circumstance; but even these a wise man will soon bring even these a wise man to bear with indifference; for what is, is; and what must be, must be.
